description:
Have you ever wondered why they are doing all this evil to us?
Because the elites don't want us to expand our consciousness. If we begin to recognize who we truly are and why we are here, it will take away their ability to enslave us. This is why they bombard us every day with fear and lies so they can lower our vibration and keep our minds occupied with things that don't matter. 
Don't let them manipulate and scare you. Master your emotions and keep your frequency high at all times. Above all, this is a war on consciousness. Don't let them win. Remember why you are here and focus on yourself and your purpose. Everything else is an illusion...
